---

<PageLayout
  title="Sobre mí"
  description="Conoce más sobre Jhoselin Quispe Luque, estudiante de Ingeniería Industrial en la Universidad Continental - Cusco."
>
  <!-- Hero Section - with background image like naisser.com -->
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full">
      <img
        src="/images/profile/fondo hero.jpg"
        alt=""
        class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
        loading="eager"
        fetchpriority="high"
      />
      <!-- Dark overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 py-16 sm:py-20 text-center">
      <!-- Profile Image - Circular -->
      <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <div class="relative w-32 h-32 sm:w-40 sm:h-40 md:w-48 md:h-48 lg:w-56 lg:h-56 mx-auto">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full border-4 border-white/80 shadow-2xl"></div>
          <img
            src="/images/profile/foto 1.jpeg"
            alt="Jhoselin Quispe Luque"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top rounded-full"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Name -->
      <h1 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3 sm:mb-4 px-4">
        <span class="text-white/95">Estudiante Ing. </span>
        <span class="text-primary">JHOSELIN QUISPE LUQUE</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Description -->
      <p class="text-white/85 text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base max-w-xl lg:max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-relaxed px-6 sm:px-4">
        Soy estudiante de Ingeniería Industrial en la Universidad Continental - Cusco, actualmente en el 5to semestre. 
        Me apasiona el análisis de procesos, la mejora continua y el uso de la tecnología para optimizar la toma de decisiones.
        En esta web quiero compartir mis proyectos y experiencias académicas contigo.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Button -->
      <a href="#profile" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-6 sm:px-8 py-2.5 sm:py-3 bg-primary text-white rounded-full text-sm sm:text-base font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg shadow-primary/30">
        Ver más
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Profile Section - naisser.com style (two columns) -->
  <section id="profile" class="section bg-white dark:bg-background">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center">
          <!-- Image side -->
          <div class="relative">
            <img
              src="/images/profile/foto 2.jpeg"
              alt="Jhoselin Quispe Luque"
              class="w-full max-w-sm sm:max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0 rounded-xl shadow-lg object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Text content -->
          <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-wide">
              JHOSELIN QUISPE LUQUE
            </h2>
            
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-muted-foreground font-medium">
              Estudiante de Ingeniería Industrial · 5to Semestre
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3">
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base italic">
                Estudio Ingeniería Industrial en la Universidad Continental - Cusco. 
                Me caracterizo por un enfoque reflexivo y analítico, buscando siempre comprender 
                el "por qué" detrás de cada problema antes de plantear soluciones.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">
                Me apasiona la mejora de procesos, el análisis de datos y la aplicación de 
                tecnologías emergentes como la Inteligencia Artificial en contextos industriales. 
                Considero el aprendizaje constante como un pilar fundamental de mi desarrollo.
              </p>
              
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base">
                He participado en diversos proyectos académicos y eventos relacionados con 
                metodologías de calidad, gestión de operaciones y optimización. Mi objetivo es 
                aplicar herramientas de ingeniería para resolver problemas reales en organizaciones.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Buttons -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 sm:gap-3 pt-2 sm:pt-4">
              <a href="/projects" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-2.5 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-200">Ver Proyectos</a>
              <a href="/events" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-2.5 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-200">Ver Eventos</a>
              <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-2.5 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all duration-200">Contactar</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services/Areas Section - naisser.com style cards -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary/30">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        {areasExpertise.map((area) => (
          <article class="service-card">
            <div class="service-card-icon">
              <svg class="w-full h-full" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d={area.icono} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="service-card-title">{area.titulo}</h3>
            <p class="service-card-description">{area.descripcion}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education Section -->
  <section class="section bg-background">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="text-foreground">Formación </span>
            <span class="text-primary">Académica</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {formacionAcademica.map((item) => (
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <span class="badge-primary text-xs">{item.periodo}</span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-700 dark:bg-green-900/30 dark:text-green-400">
                  {item.estado}
                </span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1">{item.titulo}</h3>
              <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-2 text-sm">{item.institucion}</p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed text-sm">{item.descripcion}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Skills Section -->
  <section class="section bg-secondary/30">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="text-foreground">Mis </span>
            <span class="text-primary">Habilidades</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Technical Skills -->
          <div class="card-professional">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              Habilidades Técnicas
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-5">
              {habilidadesTecnicas.map((skill) => (
                <div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between mb-2">
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">{skill.nombre}</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold">{skill.porcentaje}%</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="skill-bar">
                    <div class="skill-bar-fill" style={`width: ${skill.porcentaje}%`}></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Soft Skills -->
          <div class="card-professional">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              Habilidades Blandas
            </h3>
            <div class="space-y-5">
              {habilidadesBlandas.map((skill) => (
                <div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between mb-2">
                    <span class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground">{skill.nombre}</span>
                    <span class="text-sm text-primary font-semibold">{skill.porcentaje}%</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="skill-bar">
                    <div class="skill-bar-fill" style={`width: ${skill.porcentaje}%`}></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="section tech-pattern-bg text-white">
    <div class="hero-lines"></div>
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
          <span class="text-white">¿Quieres saber más sobre </span>
          <span class="text-primary">mis proyectos?</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm sm:text-base mb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Explora mis trabajos académicos y proyectos de mejora continua desarrollados durante mi formación.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">
            Ver Proyectos
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-5 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-2.5 border-2 border-white text-white rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition-all duration-200">
            Contactar
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
